## SpecKit Plus Commands

```bash
# Initialize project with SDD workflow
specifyplus init my-project

# Generate specification from requirements
sp.specify "Requirement description"

# Create implementation plan
sp.plan "Feature description"

# Create tasks from plan
sp.tasks "Plan details"

# Analyze implementation
sp.analyze "Implementation details"

# Check SDD status
specifyplus check

# Validate workflow progression
specifyplus validate
```

## Best Practices

1. **Always Start with Spec**: Never code without clear specifications
2. **Document Everything**: Maintain clear documentation throughout
3. **Use Git Effectively**: Each phase should have commits
4. **Review Before Proceed**: Each phase needs review before moving to next
5. **Keep Specs Updated**: Update specs as you learn more

